headline: Blackstone and TPG revive interest in buying Hologic, source says
summary: Private equity firms Blackstone and TPG revived their interest in acquiring medical diagnostics company Hologic in what could be one of the largest healthcare take-private deals this year, a person close to the transaction said on Wednesday.  Spokespeople for Blackstone and TPG declined to comment.  Hologic did not immediately respond to requests for comment.
